To set password in SCCM while deploying OS
- [ ] Open SCCM Console application
- [ ] Goto Administration
- [ ] Select Distrubution Points
- [ ] Select the distrubution point which you want to set password and goto properties
- [ ] goto PXE tab
- [ ] enable the check box [Require a password without Windows Deployment Service]
- [ ] enter the password and select apply then OK.
